data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven! The home sits on a corner lot that is a half acre of land with plenty of room to roam. The concrete block home has been well maintained. The home features no carpet. All the flooring is Pergo wood plank and tile in the bathrooms. Newer double-pane windows and AC installed in 2015 help to keep the utility bill down. Don't worry about getting cold in this home it has propane heat and 2 built-in wall heaters just in case it is really cold. The well pump was installed in 2017.  Enjoy relaxing on the big screened-in back patio. Lots of storage with 2 metal sheds and a detached garage/workshop. You will love the location nice neighborhood with NO HOA!! Easy commute to Gainesville and Alachua. Just down the road is the new San Felasco Tech City. San Felasco State Park is close by and has miles of mountain bike and horseback riding trails. Schedule your showing today!
